---
import { Button } from '@nextui-org/react';
---

<main
  class='md:text-center flex md:justify-center md:items-center flex-col z-10'
>
  <div class='md:w-1/2 pt-40'>
    <h1 class='text-6xl font-semibold mb-6'>
      Hello ðŸ‘‹, I'm a Frontend Developer
    </h1>
    <p class='text-xl font-medium text-foreground-400 mb-6'>
      As a frontend developer, I specialize in creating responsive and
      interactive user interfaces using the latest web technologies such as
      HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. I have a strong passion for building
      high-quality, visually appealing, and user-friendly websites and web
      applications
    </p>

    <Button id="download-cv" size='lg' client:visible color='primary' variant='shadow'>
      Download CV!</Button
